name: Find tag without property
description: Find all form, or any other, tags that does not contain a property set to a specific value
content:
<form>
<form action="/test">
<form action="/test" autocomplete="off">
<form action="/test" autocomplete="on">
<form autocomplete="off" action="/test">
<form autocomplete="on" action="/test">
<form autocomplete="on">
<form autocomplete="off">
author: Russell Dempsey
